textDelta: Who said, "Peace, commerce, and honest friendship with all nations, entagling alliances with none." James Madison, Abraham Lincoln, Woodrow Wilson, or Thomas Jefferson? Thomas Jefferson
Which age group worldwide has the highest HIV/AIDS death rate? Under 5, 14-May, 15-49, over 50 The age group worldwide with the highest HIV/AIDS death rate is those aged 15-49.
What is the function of skeletal muscle tissue? Skeletal muscle tissue is important for movement and energy production. It helps to produce the muscles that we use to move our bodies.
